  p.warn: :link Beware of gospel tracts which misrepresent the true biblical gospel. Some examples are shown below.
.card
  +img('IMG_0362', 'A false gospel tract')
  p: :link This tract presents the false doctrines of [Penal Substitution Atonement](#psa) (red highlights) and the [Imputed Righteousness of Christ](#irc) (purple highlight).
